# Prompts Used

## Architect Agent
"Suggest a class design for Team and MatchRecord in a Java Honor of Kings IMS. Include fields, responsibilities, and relationships with Player and Hero."

## Implementation Agent
"Implement Team.java with fields: teamName, members, heroes, wins, losses. Add methods to manage members and match results."

## Review Agent
"Review Team.java for OOP correctness, encapsulation, and potential bugs."
